OL,3,CLondon Shakespeare's Globe evacuated
OL,4,Cafter rogue flare lands among audience
OL,6,FShakespeare's Globe in London had to
OL,7,Fbe locked down and evacuated after
OL,8,Ffireworks and flares were set off from
OL,9,FMillennium Bridge on Wednesday night.
OL,11,FIt has been reported that football
OL,12,Ffans set off fireworks nearby to
OL,13,Fcelebrate the 103-year anniversary of
OL,14,Fthe Algerian football club MC Alger.
OL,16,FSocial media footage shows a dramatic
OL,17,Fdisplay in central London with red
OL,18,Fsmoke visible from afar.
