OL,3,CLondon Shakespeare's Globe evacuated
OL,4,Cafter rogue flare lands among audience
OL,6,FIt is understood that a flare fell
OL,7,Fthrough the roof, landing close to the
OL,8,Faudience at the Globe Theatre.
OL,10,FThe theatre said in a statement: "At
OL,11,F10pm on Wednesday 7 August, fireworks
OL,12,Fand flares were set off from
OL,13,FMillennium Bridge.
OL,15,F"The Globe building was immediately
OL,16,Flocked down, and the audience and
OL,17,Fcompany were invacuated and held until
OL,18,F10.50pm when the police gave notice
OL,19,Fthat it was safe to leave. All
OL,20,Faudiences, company members, and staff
OL,21,Fwere evacuated and got home safely.
