OL,6,F"We are continuing to gather the facts
OL,7,Fregarding exactly what happened. The
OL,8,FGlobe Box Office will be in contact
OL,9,Fwith all audience members who attended
OL,10,Flast night's performance."
OL,12,FMark Johnson, from Tooting, who was at
OL,13,Fthe theatre watching a performance of
OL,14,FWilliam Shakespeare's Antony and
OL,15,FCleopatra, told The Daily Mail it was
OL,16,Fa "miracle" no one was hurt, and that
OL,17,Fthere was alarm inside the theatre
OL,18,Fover the incident.
