OL,6,FHe said: "It was really confusing. It
OL,7,Ffelt like it was near the end of the
OL,8,Fperformance when we saw bright red
OL,9,Flights in the sky.
OL,11,F"Most of the audience looked up and we
OL,12,Fsaw fireworks and there was a general
OL,13,Fsense of confusion. Even the actors
OL,14,Fand actresses looked up."
OL,16,FThe theatre added: "As a major visitor
OL,17,Fdestination in London, we have
OL,18,Femergency measures in place.
