OL,6,F"These protocols were followed in a
OL,7,Fcalm and considered manner, and we
OL,8,Fwould like to thank all our audience
OL,9,Fmembers, company members, staff, and
OL,10,Fvolunteers for supporting us last
OL,11,Fnight for a safe response to the
OL,12,Fsituation."
OL,14,FThe Metropolitan Police offered no
OL,15,Fcomment.
